snippet.textDisplay:
My personal ranking till now 😬. Share yours as I would like to see what others think:

1- Jhol
2- Turri Jandi
3- O Yaara
4- Harkalay
5- Aayi Aayi
6- Maghron La
7- Chal Chaliye
8- 2AM
9- Blockbuster

There were quite a few songs which sounded meh at first but once you listen, they grow on you and you start to appreciate the subtle nuances, when you go through BTS then they become mind blowing. With Jhol and now Turri Jandi, the season is in fifth gear right now 🔥🔥🔥
